request.description:
List all ACTIVE hospitals. Any authenticated user.

Inactive hospitals are excluded — use Get All Hospitals to see them.

Success (200):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Active hospitals retrieved",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Lagos General Hospital",
      "status": "ACTIVE",
      ...
    }
  ],
  "timestamp": "..."
}

List ALL hospitals including INACTIVE ones. ADMIN only.

Use this to see deactivated hospitals and their historical data.

Success (200):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "All hospitals retrieved",
  "data": [
    { "id": 1, "status": "ACTIVE", ... },
    { "id": 2, "status": "INACTIVE", ... }
  ],
  "timestamp": "..."
}
